         <div id="title-section">

            <h2>Section 1: Get Your Access Keys</h2>
            <p>Signing up is free.</p>

         </div>

         <div class="container">

            <div>

               <h3>First you need an Amazon.com account</h3>

               <p>
			      If you have purchased anything from Amazon in the past you should already have an account. Go to 
                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com">Amazon.com</a> and sign in.
                </p>
                <p>
                    If you are new to Amazon, follow this <a href="https://www.amazon.com/ap/register/185-6171297-0635142?_encoding=UTF8&openid.assoc_handle=usflex&openid.claimed_id=http%3A%2F%2Fspecs.openid.net%2Fauth%2F2.0%2Fidentifier_select&openid.identity=http%3A%2F%2Fspecs.openid.net%2Fauth%2F2.0%2Fidentifier_select&openid.mode=checkid_setup&openid.ns=http%3A%2F%2Fspecs.openid.net%2Fauth%2F2.0&openid.ns.pape=http%3A%2F%2Fspecs.openid.net%2Fextensions%2Fpape%2F1.0&openid.pape.max_auth_age=0&openid.return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fyourstore%2Fhome%3Fie%3DUTF8%26ref_%3Dnav_custrec_newcust">link</a>
                    to sign up for a free account.
                   
                </p>
                <br><h3>Sign up for Amazon Associates</h3>
                <p>
                    Amazon Associates is a program for people to monetize their websites or blogs by linking Amazon products and service for commissions. 
                    To use the Amazon Product Advertising API you will need an Associate Tag. To get an Associate Tag you will need to sign up for Amazon Associates. 
                    Go to <a href="https://affiliate-program.amazon.com/">https://affiliate-program.amazon.com</a> and click the "Join Now for Free" button to get started. 
                </p>
                <img src="img_1_a.png" alt="Associates Sign Up"><br><br>
                
                <br><h3>Sign up for Amazon Product Advertising API</h3>
                <p>
                    Go to <a href="https://affiliate-program.amazon.com/gp/advertising/api/detail/main.html">https://affiliate-program.amazon.com/gp/advertising/api/detail/main.html</a>
                    and click the "Sign Up Now" button on the right side of the page. 
                    <br><br><img src="img_1_b.png" alt="api sign up" width="999"><br><br>
                    After you complete the signup process, click the "Manage Your Account" link. <br>
                    <br><br><img src="img_1_c.png" alt="api manage your account" width="999"><br><br>
                    Click on the "AWS Security Credentials console" link and sign in with your Amazon credentials.<br><br>
                    
                    Go to the Access Key ID and Secret Access Key section. click the "Create new Access Key" button. A pop up window
                    will appear. Cleck the "Download Key File" button. Make sure you keep this file or keep your Access Keys. After you
                    eave this screen you will not be able to access your keys again, instead you would need to create new keys. 
                    <br><br><img src="img_1_d.png" alt="access keys" width="999"><br><br>
                    Store your AWSAccessKeyID and AWSSecretKey for later use. Store your keys in a safe place and never share your keys with anyone.
                    <br><br>
                    You are all signed up and ready to start using the Amazon Product Advertising API!            
                </p>
    
